full_text:
Hi Steve,

I haven&#39;t been on the lists much lately due to a heavy Fall workload, but I wanted to let you know that I have been using your box, and getting great results. I did a session with a girl who had a loved one commit suicide, and he came through. 

I have some investigations coming up where I will be bringing my Steve&#39;s box too! 

I also asked the box about a sensitive situation with a ghost and a family, and got answers to my questions on that as well.

I know you work very hard on your boxes and they rock! The day before yesterday I was more signally challenged than usual and had the sweep set quite fast, yet clear as can be a woman&#39;s voice came through a couple of times. It could not have been stray radio signal. 

So just wanted to let you know, that I may fall way behind on the lists at the moment till I get this updating done, I am still using your box, though. Your hard work is appreciated here!

Thanks!
Draiga

